name: HONG KONG MBA DAO buy Yacht!
description: Hong Kong MBA DAO is a decentralized autonomous organization initiated by the Hong Kong MBA Institute in Hong Kong. The goal of the organization is to provide an effective and high-quality communication platform for MBA students and alumni around the world, and to gather the influence of global MBAs to achieve the most social interests of the members of the organization. Our first goal is buying a yacht in Hong Kong and we need 1500000 USD, every MBA around the world, it would be our great pleasure to have you on board!
